Hometown Selection
------------------
Some races are permitted to chose among several different
towns as their hometown.  The hometowns available for these
races give them an advantage of those without. Note that other
races have separate hometowns that are not listed here.

1. Tharnadia  - Largest city on one of the main continents,
   this is the primary home of the humans.  Tharnadia is a coastal
   city on the south west coast of its continent.

2. Sylvandawn - Located on a small forest covered continent is the primary
   home of they grey elves.  Only those of the elven, half-elven and centaur
   race can enter the city.

3. Bloodstone - This city has the reputation as a hangout for
   societies' outcasts.  Wanted killers and thieves frequent this city.
   It is located in the middle north near the coast of one of the main
   continents.

4. Shady Grove - This is the Orc home town, and Thri-Kreen are also allowed
   this town as a selection if they chose the path of evi.  Shady grove is
   located on one of the main continents, and has connections to the underdark.

5. Fort Marigot - This is the home of the Centaur race it is located on the same
    forest covered eastern continent as Sylvandawn.

6. Nax'Varan - This is the home of the Minotaur race.  It is located on the 
    main continent also shared by Bloodstone.

7. Khhiytik - This is the home town of the Thri-Kreen race, and is located on
   a main continent and located in the center of a great desert.

There are many other home towns on Duris, but all of those are pre-assined
to the race in question.

